{"tid":2116266,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"載歌載舞慶回歸 - 邁克","createTime":"2020-07-20T05:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T05:03:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fa42718ac138096a29fa8a59fbcb41442585a514","tid":2116266,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:03:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%82%81%E5%85%8B/daily/article/20200720/20959177/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2582%2581%25E5%2585%258B%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200720%2F20959177%2F&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zVuzyl20%2B4TZ9N3SWLiWM4Y%3D&h=8e7d27e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2582%2581%25E5%2585%258B%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200720%2F20959177%2F&h=30840d24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%82%81%E5%85%8B/daily/article/20200720/20959177/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n載歌載舞慶回歸 - 邁克<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200720/large/1595144135_a391.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200720%2Flarge%2F1595144135_a391.jpg&h=58833263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港各式各樣確診群組，。。。。。。。。。。「我又係老鬼，人又係老鬼，點解人哋咁夠福，我咁衰呢」，恨不得發起眾籌買張天價機票由巴黎潛返赤鱲角，哀求藍絲朋友做中間人介紹我入會，武肺第幾波都話之佢，舞照跳歌照唱，盡情玩咗先至算。貪婪的眼睛掃射歌單，負責娛賓的KK、小雪、秀秀和Royal何等等雖然聞所未聞，也不清楚唱《分飛燕》的肥媽是真肥媽抑或街上求其一個超磅嬸嬸，所謂高手出民間，絕對不嫌棄。。。。。。。。。。包括一首講人鬼情未了的《幽媾》，一首描寫舞女捨不得燈紅酒綠的《最後一夜》，還有剛剛提過的《分飛燕》，你話幾應景，最難得是他們毫不介意又分又離又陰陽阻隔唔好意頭，有種「死咪死囉」的豁達，完全當瘟疫冇到，簡直比林鄭更有資格成為天天煮的最佳榜樣。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。居然不知道壓軸的《十一哥》是什麼東東，。。。。。。。。。。失覺失覺。 <br />\n<br />\n邁克<br />\n電郵 :heartsociety2@gmail.com"}]}